867a502ad4903f9737b054278e7a9720d9bee44","tid":1783311,"uid":85822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T18:48:03.000Z","msg":"已簽 再推"},{"pid":"430b70c314910790027e4c3a4891391c511a28f3","tid":1783311,"uid":85822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T18:48:43.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ad06d652241c9ef04281d2716f8aa61fda580dcd","tid":1783311,"uid":85822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T18:49:01.000Z","msg":"再推 多你一個好多架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n借個位宣傳吸引火力黎推post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nfor 想體力升級/心態提升為民請命手足參考<br />\n補師我要幫全世界身心升level<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入黎補補正能量整理下個人狀態<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個人夠正能量先頂到落去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山 各做所長<br />\n若要勝利 必須備戰<br />\n營養＋運動 身心感覺同樣重要<br />\n<br />\n極權將破 在支爆前會係最黑暗嘅時候<br />\n幾艱難 損失都要打落去<br />\n<br />\n和理勇武強身強心飲食入門：<br />\n全世界維持健康打落去<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人人都要有自衞隊身體質素<br />\n香港人 團結反抗 無退路<br />\n未來嘅希望由我地做起<br />\n<br />\nStep 8.心理健康 正能量撚❤️<br />\n當我地遇到情況📍 在安全情況下<br />\n⚡️減少重複接觸影響自己的負面人事<br />\n🍎做自己鍾意的事<br />\n😀約定 定期運動放鬆 <br />\n🧠睇書/聽Motivation Video<br />\n🔥最緊要痴住正能量嘅朋友/人<br />\n<br />\n利申：健康教練<br />\nHerbalife  健康教練<br />\n唔係重點 重點係大家要長命幫手贏<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全民皆兵</span></span> <br />\n依家風頭火勢 好多五毛<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 團結 正能量<br />\n呢個世界唔係我地影響人<br />\n就係人地影響緊我地<br />\n我地要內在夠強 百毒不侵<br />\n<br />\n永續健康身心 長期抗爭致勝<br />\n有咩搵我幫手 免費教大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港需要你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有需TG 唔問名 <br />\n幫你Case Study <br />\n教你點飲食點運動打仗飲食法<br />\n20％運動 80％營養<br />\n學完再善用Budget 搞好自己體能<br />\n得閒係屋企/搵我做下運動放鬆<br />\n行一陣街吸哂TG 暈低仲點打落去<br />\n<br />\nMy TG<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TreeHoIsGood\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTreeHoIsGood&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWj2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=b8a370c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TreeHoIsGood</a><br />\nChannel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/treehoHealthAdvice\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FtreehoHealthAdvice&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWj2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=6e1602c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/treehoHealthAdvice</a><br />\n討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/THHATalk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTHHATalk&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWj2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=7994abbd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/THHATalk</a><br />\n長期戰爭 齊上齊落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對抗白色恐怖 <br />\n反共抗中 我地勢不兩立<br />\nWe Shall Never Surrender<br />\n<br />\nUnited, We can win the fight"},{"pid":"faf937266e697ed34d30e46baa3d9fcd1ed85540","tid":1783311,"uid":37058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T18:51:01.000Z","msg":"簽左 email confirm埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d1c9f7ea728c41b9e70dd233415bddddc1fbc2c","tid":1783311,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T18:51:08.000Z","msg":"試左幾次，得gmail收到"},{"pid":"a22a74bd03d8a2971d64cd02f9f6cfe6a64691b4","tid":1783311,"uid":309410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T18:53:03.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"f8683c327759a3e9d6efb70eea0cf921719c2258","tid":1783311,"uid":219768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T19:03:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"acd0895ec4b893e29c0ee0ea702084f5817554b3","tid":1783